官司。因为这件事情加上异地的缘故一直在冷战，我希望她对我好点，但 25 年 10 月我刷小红书发展她有了新男朋友。<br /><br />目前情况：<br />1.考研读研加她个人消费这几年我算了一下大概给出去 55 万现金。<br />2.目前已经有方案的两个案件，一个月需要还 1 万，共计一个月还 2 万，她和他妈已经半年没有给过我钱了。<br />3.第三个案件 157 万，目前还未没有判决。<br />4.收入这两年才上来，目前一年收入税前 48 万，大厂稳定有上升空间。<br />5.我今年 3 月份谈了一个女朋友，非常爱我（未坦白负债）。<br />6.我父母是农民没有工作没有养老，父亲 60 岁身体很差。<br /><br />我他妈应该怎么办😒", "last_modified": 1778825668, "replies": 394, "id": 1212953}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_large.png?m=1778522847", "name": "promotions", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_normal.png?m=1778522847", "title": "推广", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions", "topics": 11708, "footer": "", "header": "来自厂商的推广活动类主题，会被归类到这个节点。希望有情怀的产商们在发布推广内容时，主动选择发布到本节点下。点击 <a href=\"/help/node\">这里</a> 阅读 V2EX 的节点使用指南。", "title_alternative": "Promotions", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1778522847", "stars": 1263, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 864, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 606659, "username": "qiudemad", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/qiudemad", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/50b50b69400149c9ce45d427f090e18b?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/50b50b69400149c9ce45d427f090e18b?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/50b50b69400149c9ce45d427f090e18b?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1670988927, "last_modified": 1670988927, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "PtAu", "last_touched": 1778895558, "title": "[感谢管理] 虾老板中转站继续送 3000wToken", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1212875", "created": 1778810264, "deleted": 0, "content": "www.bossclaw.org 评论留邮箱就送\r\n全 pro 订阅 0.3x 倍率，全 max 订阅 2.0 倍率\r\n满血 5.5/4.7 爽蹬，纵享丝滑稳定", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"http://www.bossclaw.org\" rel=\"nofollow\">www.bossclaw.org</a> 评论留邮箱就送\n全 pro 订阅 0.3x 倍率，全 max 订阅 2.0 倍率\n满血 5.5/4.7 爽蹬，纵享丝滑稳定</p>\n", "last_modified": 1778810264, "replies": 210, "id": 1212875}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10832, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2312, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 645780, "username": "leguandexincheng", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/leguandexincheng", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ff185c1c8dba720d57b6b2ba35f3a7dc?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ff185c1c8dba720d57b6b2ba35f3a7dc?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ff185c1c8dba720d57b6b2ba35f3a7dc?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1693201381, "last_modified": 1776663649, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "wetalk", "last_touched": 1778894211, "title": "诚邀已婚有娃男性朋友，探讨中年阶段的困惑[中登专属]", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1212877", "created": 1778810807, "deleted": 0, "content": "# 当你在凝视深渊的时候，深渊也在凝视你，未婚女性不建议阅读，更不要点评和抨击。\r\n\r\n## 基本情况\r\n   - 1.90 年男，已婚两娃，有房有车，无贷款，现金 50+，股票 50+；\r\n   - 2.不抽烟不嚼槟榔，偶尔小酌，作息规律；\r\n   - 3.定居长沙，家庭生活开销不高，小孩是普通的公办学校，炒股收益基本覆盖开销；\r\n   - 4.目前没自己的事业，工作属于苟着的状态。\r\n     \r\n## 目前困惑\r\n   - 1.沉迷青春的气息，精力投入占据 20%估计，时间占用也不少。\r\n\r\n## 相关经历\r\n   - 1.吃过蛋炒饭，玉兰路、二街、海鲜市场都去过，属于低频；\r\n   - 2.楼凤，梅溪湖、滨江、五一、汇金、星沙等，属于高频；\r\n   - 3.专车，周边市、长沙市，包天、周，这两年 80%。\r\n\r\n     \r\n## 探讨\r\n   - 1.如何走出来或者改变这个情况？\r\n     如何用一场更有趣的成年人的冒险，去置换一场虚无的青春猎艳？\r\n\r\n## 期望\r\n   - 1.不做道德上点评，抨击；\r\n   - 2.不讨论各种细节，提供联系方式；\r\n   - 3.想和有类似经历的老哥们理性深度讨论这个情况。", "content_rendered": "<h1>当你在凝视深渊的时候，深渊也在凝视你，未婚女性不建议阅读，更不要点评和抨击。</h1>\n<h2>基本情况</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1.90 年男，已婚两娃，有房有车，无贷款，现金 50+，股票 50+；</li>\n<li>2.不抽烟不嚼槟榔，偶尔小酌，作息规律；</li>\n<li>3.定居长沙，家庭生活开销不高，小孩是普通的公办学校，炒股收益基本覆盖开销；</li>\n<li>4.目前没自己的事业，工作属于苟着的状态。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>目前困惑</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1.沉迷青春的气息，精力投入占据 20%估计，时间占用也不少。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>相关经历</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1.吃过蛋炒饭，玉兰路、二街、海鲜市场都去过，属于低频；</li>\n<li>2.楼凤，梅溪湖、滨江、五一、汇金、星沙等，属于高频；</li>\n<li>3.专车，周边市、长沙市，包天、周，这两年 80%。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>探讨</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1.如何走出来或者改变这个情况？\n如何用一场更有趣的成年人的冒险，去置换一场虚无的青春猎艳？</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>期望</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1.不做道德上点评，抨击；</li>\n<li>2.不讨论各种细节，提供联系方式；</li>\n<li>3.想和有类似经历的老哥们理性深度讨论这个情况。</li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1778810807, "replies": 203, "id": 1212877}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 10832, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2312, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 341441, "username": "superJava", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/superJava", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c5e44e50eaad93afe4bddac7df6fc2da?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c5e44e50eaad93afe4bddac7df6fc2da?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c5e44e50eaad93afe4bddac7df6fc2da?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1534323026, "last_modified": 1776654460, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "rykiechin", "last_touched": 1778892064, "title": "为什么大家对瓢虫的容忍度比对表妹要高得多", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1212914", "created": 1778815130, "deleted": 0, "content": "看这两个热帖，让我不太能理解的是，表妹被骂了二百多楼，瓢虫就算不认同的回复也比较 peace 。\r\n这种舆论反差让我挺困惑的，在情、理、法上面，瓢虫都比表妹要严重得多吧，但舆论却是反着的，为什么会是这样的舆论，是有两套道德标准还是大家觉得后者比前者更严重呢，还是一些其他的什么原因。", "content_rendered": "看这两个热帖，让我不太能理解的是，表妹被骂了二百多楼，瓢虫就算不认同的回复也比较 peace 。<br />这种舆论反差让我挺困惑的，在情、理、法上面，瓢虫都比表妹要严重得多吧，但舆论却是反着的，为什么会是这样的舆论，是有两套道德标准还是大家觉得后者比前者更严重呢，还是一些其他的什么原因。", "last_modified": 1778825696, "replies": 111, "id": 1212914}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_large.png?m=1778522847", "name": "promotions", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_normal.png?m=1778522847", "title": "推广", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions", "topics": 11708, "footer": "", "header": "来自厂商的推广活动类主题，会被归类到这个节点。希望有情怀的产商们在发布推广内容时，主动选择发布到本节点下。点击 <a href=\"/help/node\">这里</a> 阅读 V2EX 的节点使用指南。", "title_alternative": "Promotions", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1778522847", "stars": 1263, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 864, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 669406, "username": "briver123", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/briver123", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ddfb6de626ddd03957dffd1072af29cb?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ddfb6de626ddd03957dffd1072af29cb?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ddfb6de626ddd03957dffd1072af29cb?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1704194645, "last_modified": 1704194645, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "zhiyu1998", "last_touched": 1778875409, "title": "GPT 试用时代结束了， Codex 中转站 送 2000w Token", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1212987", "created": 1778829124, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天传出 GPT 试用结束了，后续估计没有试用了\r\n\r\n上周，买了几个正价 Pro 会员，没什么人用，目前还没有回本，希望大佬们需要的支持一下\r\n\r\n目前号池由 Team 、Plus 和 Pro 20x 组成，后续拉闸了准备入手多个 Pro 账号，目前卖的也是比较的便宜\r\n\r\n每张卡赠送 5 刀，倍率比较低\r\n\r\n中转站网址： https://1024token.club\r\n\r\n评论区留邮箱赠送\r\n\r\n希望觉得好用的大佬可以留下来，谢谢", "content_rendered": "今天传出 GPT 试用结束了，后续估计没有试用了<br /><br />上周，买了几个正价 