png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3671, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 109210, "username": "zcm3579", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zcm3579", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5b8b/215d/109210_mini.png?m=1578390556", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5b8b/215d/109210_normal.png?m=1578390556", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5b8b/215d/109210_large.png?m=1578390556", "created": 1428200846, "last_modified": 1578390556, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "lixon166", "last_touched": 1778872716, "title": "企业裁员人选问题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1212921", "created": 1778815912, "deleted": 0, "content": "假如公司开发部有 10 人\r\n\r\n - 4 个技术水平普通 薪资普通\r\n - 2 个技术水平普通中上 薪资高(约是上面的 1.5~2 倍)\r\n - 1 个技术部负责人(技术水平中上) 薪资最高\r\n - 1 个技术差 薪资最低的小年轻\r\n - 2 个测试人员\r\n\r\n实际维持业务只需要普通技术的人员\r\n现在需要裁员, 大家会怎么选择人选", "content_rendered": "<p>假如公司开发部有 10 人</p>\n<ul>\n<li>4 个技术水平普通 薪资普通</li>\n<li>2 个技术水平普通中上 薪资高(约是上面的 1.5~2 倍)</li>\n<li>1 个技术部负责人(技术水平中上) 薪资最高</li>\n<li>1 个技术差 薪资最低的小年轻</li>\n<li>2 个测试人员</li>\n</ul>\n<p>实际维持业务只需要普通技术的人员\n现在需要裁员, 大家会怎么选择人选</p>\n", "last_modified": 1778818966, "replies": 60, "id": 1212921}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1691642161", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1691642161", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 18704, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1691642161", "stars": 8235, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 411532, "username": "clacf", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/clacf", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a5af21f8dc33efc660faf5fb6b18aff?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a5af21f8dc33efc660faf5fb6b18aff?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9a5af21f8dc33efc660faf5fb6b18aff?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1557638602, "last_modified": 1775539032, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "wwwz", "last_touched": 1778879220, "title": "放弃 tun 模式，拥抱 ProxyBridge，网络瞬间流畅了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1212904", "created": 1778814168, "deleted": 0, "content": "真的累了，折腾各种方案来优化 clash 的 tun 模式速度，包括不限于 fake ip, 自建 dns ，dns 缓存，尝试各种 stack 。都不尽人意，总是会发生各种各样的问题，最大的问题，还是莫名卡顿（我是日本 vps 上自建的代理服务器，tuic 协议的）。\r\n\r\n今天尝试了 ProxyBridge ，关闭 tun 模式，把需要代理的 windows 工具挂上，顿时，我的电脑像换了一个似的，各种网站快的飞起。项目地址是： https://github.com/InterceptSuite/ProxyBridge", "content_rendered": "真的累了，折腾各种方案来优化 clash 的 tun 模式速度，包括不限于 fake ip, 自建 dns ，dns 缓存，尝试各种 stack 。都不尽人意，总是会发生各种各样的问题，最大的问题，还是莫名卡顿（我是日本 vps 上自建的代理服务器，tuic 协议的）。<br /><br />今天尝试了 ProxyBridge ，关闭 tun 模式，把需要代理的 windows 工具挂上，顿时，我的电脑像换了一个似的，各种网站快的飞起。项目地址是： <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/InterceptSuite/ProxyBridge\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://github.com/InterceptSuite/ProxyBridge</a>", "last_modified": 1778819015, "replies": 56, "id": 1212904}]